# Link Diagnostics Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   analyze_link_health — Analyze overall health of a transport link
#   get_link_history — Get historical events and outage data for a link
#   run_link_diagnostics — Run OTDR, loopback, or BER diagnostics on a link
